Article

Using Metadynamics To Explore the Free Energy of Dewetting in Biologically Relevant Nanopores
Erik B. Nordquist,§ Samantha A. Schultz,§ and Jianhan Chen*

Cite This: J. Phys. Chem. B 2022, 126, 6428−6437

Read Online

Downloaded via UNIV OF MASSACHUSETTS AMHERST on September 9, 2022 at 22:15:20 (UTC). See https://pubs.acs.org/sharingguidelines for options on how to legitimately share published articles.

